>I am having problems reading some of the handwritten dimensions. I was
>wondering if anyone has made one of these recently and knows the dimensions.
>What I need is
>  1.. The overall length of Piece A - the right side of the piece as shown in
>the drawing (looks like either 3 7/8 or 3 7/16).
>  2.. The overall length of Piece B (although this might not be as critical as
>piece A).
>  3.. The height of Piece A (looks like 1 1/4 or 1 1/2)
>  4.. The height of the upper holes in Piece A ( 3/4 ? )
>I can wait until I have the engine apart and figure it out but I would like to
